移动浏览器访问其<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://pikmin-finder.nintendo.net/">网站</a>，然后开始在手机上捕捉皮克敏。您还可以扫描在桌面浏览器上打开网站时显示的二维码。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/nintendos-new-mobile-game-lets-you-pluck-pikmin-on-your-browser-064423362.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ce7445db-6d28-444a-8b98-b1d51cdc7302</guid><dc:creator>玛丽埃拉·穆恩</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 05 Sep 2023 06:44:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693896245</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T06:44:09+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Utility Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[Personal Finance - Career & Education]]></category><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Handheld & Connected Devices]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Mariella Moon]]></category><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/83803990-4bb0-11ee-bf6d-199b1c5976db" width="1280"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="720" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/83803990-4bb0-11ee-bf6d-199b1c5976db" width="1280"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Business Wire]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA["Pikmin Short Movies" Pikmin are a mysterious mix of plant and animal. Captain Olimar is an astronaut who happens to come to their planet. Pikmin live together with him and collect various treasures on the planet. Pikmin come out from their game world and appear in a CG animation film. This omnibus film contains three short episodes: "The Night Juicer," in which Captain Olimar makes his favorite juice; "Treasures in a Bottle," in which Pikmin meet a strange treasure; "Occupational Hazards," a big adventure at a construction site. (C)Nintendo]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[27th Tokyo International Film Festival Welcomes "Father of Super Mario" Shigeru Miyamoto (Nintendo Game Producer) to Screen "PIKMIN Short Movies"]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2 returns from the shadows with a new developer]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>两年前，Paradox Interactive 与该游戏的前开发商 Hardsuit Labs 分道扬镳，并<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-indefinite-delay-165029556.html"><ins>无限期推迟了该游戏</ins></a>，两年后<em>，《吸血鬼：避世血统 2》</em>已从开发地狱的深渊中崛起。出版商此后招募了<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-08-dear-esther-ios-release.html"><em><ins>《亲爱的埃丝特》</ins></em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2015-04-16-everybodys-gone-to-the-rapture-trailer-song.html"><em><ins>每个人都沉浸在狂喜</ins></em></a>之中<em>&nbsp;</em> The Chinese Room 工作室正在开发 2004 年原版 RPG 的续作<em>。《血族 2》</em>预计将于 2024 年秋季推出。</p><p> Chinese Room 保留了一些原始概念，同时抛弃了其他概念，以自己的愿景重新构建<em>《血统 2》</em> 。现代西雅图的场景以及 Hardsuit 的一些关卡和艺术设计都得以保留。然而，创意总监 Alex Skidmore 告诉<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.pcgamer.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-has-been-quietly-rebuilt-by-dear-esther-developer-the-chinese-room-with-different-gameplay-mechanics-and-rpg-systems/"><em><ins>PC Gamer</ins></em></a> ，该游戏现在拥有“一个具有不同游戏机制和 RPG 系统的新代码库。”你将扮演一个年长的吸血鬼，而不是你<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2014-11-24-ccp-games-kills-a-fan-remake-of-vampire-the-masquerade-bloodl.html"><ins>在原版游戏中</ins></a>可能熟悉的新鲜面孔。虽然主角已经停滞了一段时间，所以你会和他们同时适应寒冷的环境。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="6f61d3d840d24f438f93917cfbcb205b"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2clSTM3UvTo?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p>对于 The Chinese Room 来说，这是一种新的挑战，到目前为止，The Chinese Room 一直专注于充满神秘感的大气步行模拟器，正如<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.polygon.com/23858293/perhaps-vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-release-date-developer-the-chinese-room"><em><ins>Polygon</ins></em></a>所言<em>&nbsp;</em>笔记。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade-bloodlines-2-delayed-2021-200243795.html"><ins>就像它的最新项目一样，</ins></a>该工作室多年来也经历了自己的麻烦。 2017 年，由于资金问题，该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2017-09-24-everybodys-gone-to-the-rapture-creator-goes-dark.html"><ins>几乎完全关闭，</ins></a>随后 Sumo Digital 接手并重振了它（Sumo Digital 本身后来<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tencent-sumo-acquisition-091425058.html"><ins>找到了新的所有者，即腾讯</ins></a>）。</p><p>在接下来的几个月里，我们将进一步了解 The Chinese Room 为粉丝们准备的内容。 Paradox 计划在一月份更深入地讨论<em>《吸血鬼：避世血统 2》</em> 。 </p><div id="946bc5f1956341c7813e01154950499b"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/D6b6LGubq6I?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade---bloodlines-2-returns-from-the-shadows-with-a-new-developer-200008403.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/vampire-the-masquerade---bloodlines-2-returns-from-the-shadows-with-a-new-developer-200008403.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 85cea5bc-5ffe-49aa-91ba-0b4a11924115</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 20:00:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693856416</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T19:40:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Personal Investing Ideas & Strategies]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/c744a000-4b59-11ee-92bd-ae17a3d99cbe" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1080" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/c744a000-4b59-11ee-92bd-ae17a3d99cbe" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[The Chinese Room/Paradox Interactive]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A wintry nighttime setting in a city in Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[A wintry nighttime setting in a city in Vampire: The Masquerade - Bloodlines 2]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Final Fantasy XVI is coming to PC, Square Enix confirms]]></title><d