s-ready-for-new-ev-platforms/"><ins>这是梅赛德斯正在开发的专有电池技术</ins></a>。该平台不太可能在 2025 年之前出现在车辆中，这意味着更小、更便宜的 G 级电动汽车最早将于 2026 年发布。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/mercedes-benz-teases-a-smaller-cheaper-g-wagon-luxury-ev-173321784.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/mercedes-benz-teases-a-smaller-cheaper-g-wagon-luxury-ev-173321784.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a857087b-c7cf-4db6-b645-f9fc42adb8cc</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 17:33:21 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693848802</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T17:33:26+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/9a6a8bf0-4b43-11ee-9feb-8901f419cd12" width="2035"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1200" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/9a6a8bf0-4b43-11ee-9feb-8901f419cd12" width="2035"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Mercedes-Benz]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An image of a G-Wagon EV prototype.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Mercedes G-Class EV]]></media:title></media:cont