und like a big change, but it is because it should improve durability while also putting less stress on the screen when it folds.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Z Fold 5 bottom]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Spotify reportedly locks white noise podcasters out of an ad program]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>据称<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/spotify/">，Spotify</a>与白噪音播客制造商的关系紧张已经有一段时间了，现在该公司似乎正在对他们采取更多行动。据<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-01/spotify-to-limit-white-noise-podcasters-money-making-options" data-original-link="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-09-01/spotify-to-limit-white-noise-podcasters-money-making-options"><em>彭博社报道</em></a>，从 10 月 1 日起，白噪音播客将<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/4/23858268/spotify-ambient-white-noise-podcasts-ad-revenue-crackdown" data-original-link="https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/4/23858268/spotify-ambient-white-noise-podcasts-ad-revenue-crackdown">不再有资格</a>参加 Spotify 的大使广告计划。</p><p>根据该计划，Spotify 向播客付费，让其阅读该公司自有产品的广告。其目标是让更多人为该平台制作节目。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p><em>彭博社</em>此前报道称，一些白噪音播客每月的收入高达 18,000 美元，这在很大程度上是由于 Spotify 自己向他们支付了广告投放费用。 <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/spotify-almost-removed-white-noise-podcasts-to-save-money-065639545.html">最近有消息称</a>，该公司考虑将这些类型的播客从其平台上完全撤下，因为它们会导致其年毛利润减少 3800 万美元。</p><p>报告称，大使广告在白噪音播客上效果不佳，因为听众通常不像对话或叙事播客那样投入。据报道，据说他们是更被动的听众，他们为了背景噪音而播放这些节目，因此 Spotify 并没有从这些广告中看到太多好处。</p><p>白噪音播客的制作者仍然可以通过听众的直接支持、付费会员资格和自动广告来赚钱。但此举正在切断一个重要的收入来源。另一方面，对于那些只想听叽叽喳喳的鸟儿或雷暴雨而不被推广<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/anchor/">Spotify 播客工具</a>之类的人打扰的听众来说，这可能是有益的。</p><p>此外，Spotify还提高了大使广告的资格门槛。播客现在需要在 60 天内拥有 1,000 名唯一听众（之前为 100 名）才能参与该计划。</p><p>该公司还计划邀请更多播客加入其自动广告计划。 Spotify 表示，它将与播客运营商将这些广告的收入分成两半，一改之前根据展示次数支付统一费率的做法。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/spotify-reportedly-locks-white-noise-podcasters-out-of-an-ad-program-150124532.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/spotify-reportedly-locks-white-noise-podcasters-out-of-an-ad-program-150124532.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 02a5dc2d-fc74-4c49-ab5e-1fbc4a044b8c</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 15:01:24 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693903850</ingested><modified> 2023-09-05T08:50:59+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="3840" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/94653c40-4b30-11ee-ad5f-9c4d529acd74" width="5760"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="3840" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/94653c40-4b30-11ee-ad5f-9c4d529acd74" width="5760"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[FILE - In this Tuesday, April 3, 2018 file photo, a trading post sports the Spotify logo on the floor of the New York Stock Exchange. U.K. regulators are stepping up scrutiny of the country's music streaming market to see whether there's enough competition, after lawmakers outlined concerns that big online major platforms like Spotify may be too dominant. The U.K.'s competition watchdog said Tuesday, Oct. 19 2021 it will carry out a “market study” to assess whether fresh measures are needed to improve streaming competition. (AP Photo/Richard Drew, File)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Britain Music Streaming]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Volkswagen will produce an EV version of its GTI hot hatch]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>大众汽车的 ID 产品线目前已经相当充实，包括从 ID.2all 紧凑型到 ID.4 跨界车等各种车型，但热销车型在哪里呢？大众汽车通过 ID.GTI 概念车<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.volkswagen-newsroom.com/en/press-releases/sporty-electric-emotive-volkswagen-presents-the-id-gti-concept-show-car-17584">回答了这个问题</a>，这是一款最终将投入生产的电动掀背车。</p><p>就像启发它的原始 GTI 一样（“I”不再代表喷射，而是“智能”），它是一款运动型、紧凑型掀背车，看起来静止不动。从尺寸来看，它比现款高尔夫 GTI 更短但更高，内部空间也稍大一些。 ID.GTI 基于（并且非常相似） <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/vws-id2all-compact-ev-will-cost-under-25000-when-it-arrives-in-2025-194635462.html">ID.2all 紧凑型</a>，增加了 20 英寸车轮、前、侧和后扰流板、后扩散器、蜂窝格栅、条纹图形、LED 雾灯等功能。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6dd5e520-4b08-11ee-863e-a23359fc4b38" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/6dd5e520-4b08-11ee-863e-a23359fc4b38" style="height:675px;width:1200px;" alt="大众汽车将生产 GTI 掀背车的 EV 版本" data-uuid="9d542444-2c26-3611-ac6f-cb2f553bf4e6"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">大众汽车</div></figure><p>它还将进行操控和性能调整，但大众没有提供任何细节。 ID.2all 配备 223HP 电机，可在 7 秒内加速 62MPH，预计续航里程为 280 英里。不过，ID.GTI 很可能轻松击败这些数字，而且最高速度也应该更快。</p><p>大众确实表示 ID.GTI 将配备电子控制前轴差速锁，提供牵引力控制，就像当前的高尔夫 GTI 一样。该公司写道，它的工作效果会更好，“因为与任何电力系统一样，电力驱动电机的设置几乎可以无限变化。”由于电池位于车辆地板中，它的重心也较低，有助于操控。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/091ed060-4b08-11ee-bdbf-ccade7db78ce" data-crop-orig-src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/091ed060-4b08-11ee-bdbf-ccade7db78ce" style="height:1010px;width:1795px;" alt="大众 ID.GTI" data-uuid="21a9fb43-2ea0-395a-baf5-beae9a3f37b4"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">大众汽车</div></figure><p>ID.GTI概念车的内部配备了格子呢运动座椅、驱动选择器、运动型方向盘、10.9英寸仪表盘以及12.9英寸信息娱乐系统。它还配备了 AR 平视显示器，可为驾驶员和前排乘客投影速度甚至赛道布局等信息。特殊的 GTI 按钮可激活红色照明方案。</p><p>大众表示将生产 ID.GTI 概念车，但没有透露何时或售价如何。不过，它很有可能会与 ID.2all 大约同时上市，ID.2all 的售价低于 30,000 美元，预计于 2025 年发布。 </p><div id="59ef90f6d04a420ab6e7423c761052d9"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bMERyOqUpNA?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/volkswagen-will-product-an-ev-version-of-its-gti-hot-hatch-130029312.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/volkswagen-will-produce-an-ev-version-of-its-gti-hot-hatch-130029312.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 20f5421f-8c33-4389-a423-87f6af134984</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Mon, 04 Sep 2023 13:00:29 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1693821518</ingested><modified> 2023-09-04T09:58:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Autos]]></category><category><![CDATA[Transportation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="1197" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-09/d0ee5eb0-4b00-11ee-b79d-3c3929b1290a" width="1795"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier>